@page "/quality"

<PageTitle>Quality Standards - YasirSteel</PageTitle>

<!-- Page Header -->
<section class="hero" style="min-height: 40vh; padding: 4rem 0;">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="hero-content">
            <h1>Quality & Standards</h1>
            <p>Uncompromising commitment to excellence through rigorous quality control and international standard compliance.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<!-- Quality Philosophy -->
<section class="page-section section-white">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="quality-content">
            <div>
                <h2 style="font-size: 2.5rem; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; color: #1e3c72;">Our Quality Philosophy</h2>
                <p style="font-size: 1.1rem; color: #666; margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">
                    At YasirSteel, quality is not just a goal—it's the foundation of everything we do. Our comprehensive quality management system ensures that every product leaving our facility meets or exceeds the highest international standards.
                </p>
                <p style="font-size: 1.1rem; color: #666; margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">
                    We believe that consistent quality is achieved through systematic processes, continuous monitoring, advanced testing equipment, and a team committed to excellence. Our quality assurance program covers every aspect of production, from raw material inspection to final product delivery.
                </p>
                <p style="font-size: 1.1rem; color: #666;">
                    Our state-of-the-art quality control department is equipped with electronic testing equipment and staffed by experienced professionals who ensure that every product meets stringent quality requirements before dispatch.
                </p>
            </div>
            <div class="about-stats">
                <div class="stat-item">
                    <div class="stat-number">100%</div>
                    <div class="stat-label">Quality Inspection</div>
                </div>
                <div class="stat-item">
                    <div class="stat-number">ISO</div>
                    <div class="stat-label">Certified Processes</div>
                </div>
                <div class="stat-item">
                    <div class="stat-number">24/7</div>
                    <div class="stat-label">Quality Monitoring</div>
                </div>
                <div class="stat-item">
                    <div class="stat-number">99.8%</div>
                    <div class="stat-label">Customer Satisfaction</div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<!-- Quality Features -->
<section class="page-section section-gray">
    <div class="container">
        <h2 class="section-title">Quality Assurance Features</h2>
        <div class="services-grid">
            <div class="service-card">
                <div class="service-icon">🔬</div>
                <h3>Advanced Testing Laboratory</h3>
                <p>Our in-house testing laboratory is equipped with state-of-the-art equipment for comprehensive material testing including tensile strength, yield strength, elongation, and chemical composition analysis.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="service-card">
                <div class="service-icon">📊</div>
                <h3>Statistical Process Control</h3>
                <p>Implementation of statistical process control methods to monitor and control manufacturing processes, ensuring consistent quality and early detection of any variations.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="service-card">
                <div class="service-icon">✅</div>
                <h3>Multi-Stage Inspection</h3>
                <p>Rigorous inspection at multiple stages of production including raw material inspection, in-process quality checks, and final product verification before dispatch.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="service-card">
                <div class="service-icon">📜</div>
                <h3>Comprehensive Documentation</h3>
                <p>Detailed documentation and traceability for all products including material certificates, test reports, and quality assurance records for complete transparency.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="service-card">
                <div class="service-icon">👨‍🔬</div>
                <h3>Expert Quality Team</h3>
                <p>Dedicated team of quality control professionals with extensive experience in steel manufacturing and international quality standards compliance.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="service-card">
                <div class="service-icon">🔄</div>
                <h3>Continuous Improvement</h3>
                <p>Regular review and enhancement of quality processes based on customer feedback, industry best practices, and technological advancements.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<!-- International Standards -->
<section class="page-section section-white">
    <div class="container">
        <h2 class="section-title">International Standards Compliance</h2>
        <div class="quality-content">
            <div class="quality-features">
                <div class="feature-item">
                    <div class="feature-icon">🏆</div>
                    <div>
                        <strong>ISO 9001:2015 Quality Management</strong><br>
                        Certified quality management system ensuring consistent processes and customer satisfaction
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="feature-item">
                    <div class="feature-icon">🔍</div>
                    <div>
                        <strong>ASTM International Standards</strong><br>
                        Compliance with American Society for Testing and Materials specifications for steel products
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="feature-item">
                    <div class="feature-icon">📏</div>
                    <div>
                        <strong>British Standards (BS 4483)</strong><br>
                        Adherence to British Standards for steel fabric reinforcement specifications
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="feature-item">
                    <div class="feature-icon">⚡</div>
                    <div>
                        <strong>DIN Standards Compliance</strong><br>
                        Meeting German Industrial Standards for steel reinforcement and wire mesh products
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="feature-item">
                    <div class="feature-icon">🎯</div>
                    <div>
                        <strong>ACI Code Requirements</strong><br>
                        Compliance with American Concrete Institute building code requirements for structural concrete
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="feature-item">
                    <div class="feature-icon">🌟</div>
                    <div>
                        <strong>Saudi Standards Authority (SSA)</strong><br>
                        Meeting regional standards and specifications for construction materials
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div>
                <h3 style="font-size: 2rem; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; color: #1e3c72;">Quality Testing Procedures</h3>
                <p style="font-size: 1.1rem; color: #666; margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">
                    Our comprehensive testing procedures ensure that every product meets the specified requirements and performance criteria. We conduct the following tests as per international standards:
                </p>

                <ul style="font-size: 1rem; color: #666; margin-bottom: 2rem; padding-left: 1.5rem;">
                    <li><strong>Tensile Strength Testing:</strong> Verification of ultimate tensile strength and yield strength</li>
                    <li><strong>Elongation Testing:</strong> Measurement of ductility and deformation characteristics</li>
                    <li><strong>Chemical Composition Analysis:</strong> Spectroscopic analysis of chemical composition</li>
                    <li><strong>Dimensional Verification:</strong> Precise measurement of dimensions and tolerances</li>
                    <li><strong>Surface Quality Inspection:</strong> Visual and automated inspection of surface conditions</li>
                    <li><strong>Weld Quality Testing:</strong> Specific tests for welded wire mesh products</li>
                    <li><strong>Bend Testing:</strong> Verification of bending properties and crack resistance</li>
                </ul>

                <p style="font-size: 1.1rem; color: #666;">
                    All test results are documented and test certificates are provided with shipments upon request. Our quality documentation ensures complete traceability and compliance verification for every product.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

